text:
I did it too, a letter to Santa...
But it was harder than I thought.
You really thought about it, didn't you?

Yeah.
I even thought about writing down what I wanted.

...I ended up overthinking it,
and it turned into more like a declaration.

...But I understand
I think mine ended up more like a year-end greeting...!

Oh, Chiyoko too...?
I wonder if both of us will surprise Santa...!
